<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>gẖnwạ mʿạyạ yạ sẖʿb ạlrb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- gẖnwạ mʿạyạ yạ sẖʿb ạlrb ..tʿạlwạ nrnm lyh
 kẖlwạ htạf tsbyḥnạ ydwy .. wyʿln nṣrnạ fyh
 wlywm mjyỷh nkwn .. sẖʿbh ạlly mstnyh
 wmʿạh hnạk fy smạh .. nfḍl nrnm lyh
 1- qlby byhtf lly fdạny .. bdmh ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 rwḥy wʿqly wyạ lsạny .. yʿẓmwạ ạ̉gẖly̱ ḥbyb
 bsjwd wḥmd wʿwd .. hạmjd ạsmh wạ̉ʿlyh
 wf lyl zmạn ạlgẖrbẗ .. yfḍl qlby yrnm lyh
 2- wsṭ ạlḥrb wwqt ạlḍyq .. ạ̉nạ bạ̉rfʿ qlby ạ̹lyh
 wʿdh ytẖbt fy ạ̹ymạny .. ykẖlyny ạ̉htf lyh
 dy qywd sjwn wjywsẖ ḥrwb .. nksrhạ bạltsbyḥ
 lmạ byʿlạ htạf ạ̹ymạnnạ .. mjdaⁿạ llmsyḥ
 3- mjd ạlrb fy wsṭ knysth .. bnʿlnh bạltsbyḥ
 wbạ̉ṣwạt ạlḥmd bnhtf .. ʿlwạ ạsm ạlmsyḥ
 rạfʿyn ṣlyb ạlrb .. dh ạ̹ḥnạ bdmh mfdyyn
 gẖạlbyn jnwd ạlsẖr bạsmh .. wdạymaⁿạ mntṣryn</lyrics>
